msgid "Tags"
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:11
# 8dc48bf0b480455e87702ef619ffda19
msgid "Like folders, tags is a way to separate and organize Emails. Tags are showing up as a colored reference in the subject line of the referenced Emails."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:15
# 8f9300e9b466481ca01abbccca58b74c
msgid "Tags can be reused across the Kolab components - Email, Calendar, Notes, Files and Tasks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:19
# f9d9d4941dc4470ca70efb2dba17ebe0
msgid "When a tag is associated with a number of Emails, these Emails can be listed by clicking the tag in the tag-cloud. It is possible to select more than one tag using CTRL key. This way one can display messages associated with all selected tags."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:22
# dcb4832f54f04afeb4c3072500ce6a81
msgid "The tag-cloud can be found under the :ref:`folder list <mail-folders>` in the Email view. It is showing all available tags."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:28
# 9ff403451b5a43d4ad6384aede45348c
msgid "Creating a tag"
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:30
# 4a2a148e04614be480d412a3f9a1403c
msgid "Tags can be created, either from the manage menu (see above) or from the dropdown menu in the mail view. Rightclick on an Email in the list, and select \"Mark -> Tag as...\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:36
# b01add6c2a734d60ae7f65ddbffd3b4b
msgid "Managing tags"
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:38
# 4c986569129c4ca087363341d6becbf7
msgid "Tags can be managed through the menu in the tag-cloud. The menu is opened by clicking the wheel in the buttom of the tag-cloud. Here you can add/remove tags or modify their name and color."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:41
# ae55ddb468b54934a3997e399664c2aa
msgid "Tags are associated to Email messages via the drop-down menu in the Email list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:45
# c9882b94e0fd41328b2e18f21721eb63
msgid "Deleting tags"
msgstr ""

#: ../../en_US/_plugins/kolab_tags/mail.rst:47
# c738c03404424c7b989095468961e5dd
msgid "A tag which is no longer needed can be removed via the tag-cloud menu. This will remove the tag from the cloud and the references to the associated Emails. The Emails will however remain."
msgstr ""

